title: [Guardian Keep, Inner Wall]
description: The tall outer wall on the eastern side of this grassy courtyard joins up with the massive inner wall of the keep.  The presence of elven militia can be seen wandering the sunlit paths that exist between the many tents and kiosks that have been set up in this area.

The tall outer wall on the eastern side of this grass-filled sward joins up with the massive inner wall of the keep to the north.  The presence of elven militia can be seen wandering the moonlit shadows that exist between the many multicolored kiosks and tents that have been set up in this protected area.
